{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"title":"PinCodeInputComponentTokens Implementations","role":"collectionGroup","roleHeading":"API Collection"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemepincodeinputcomponenttokensprovider\/pincodeinputcomponenttokens-implementations"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider"]]},"topicSections":[{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/sizeMaxWidth","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/sizeMinWidth","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/spaceColumnGapDigitInput"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true}],"kind":"article","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/PinCodeInputComponentTokens-Implementations"},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of pin code input"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSPinCodeInput"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllPinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PinceCodeInputComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"pin code input"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pin code input"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of dimensions (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemepincodeinputcomponenttokensprovider","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider/spaceColumnGapDigitInput":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token spaces.columnGapMedium"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spaceColumnGapDigitInput"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","text":"SpaceSemanticToken"}],"title":"spaceColumnGapDigitInput","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemepincodeinputcomponenttokensprovider\/spacecolumngapdigitinput","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/spaceColumnGapDigitInput"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider/sizeMaxWidth":{"type":"topic","title":"sizeMaxWidth","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sizeMaxWidth"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","text":"SizeSemanticToken"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text"